{"tid":771212,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"又係我，我又失眠","createTime":"2018-08-07T17:45:52.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-13T10:32:53.000Z","uid":37358,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"c3777ed3eace6ac0d81b154d75ee021aa829280b","tid":771212,"uid":37358,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-07T17:45:52.000Z","msg":"先講返我少少背景先：<br />\n<br />\n自從我開始返工之後，個人就好易失眠，返咗3個星期工，有2個星期係有嚴重失眠，即係每隔一晚到就瞓唔著。唔知點解每次一上到床，個人硬係進入唔到朦朦朧朧個狀態，成日又賴個枕頭太高太低，又賴個冷氣唔夠凍，總之成個人係好難進入到訓覺嘅狀態，唔知自己想點。<br />\n<br />\n唔知點解我一係張床一瞓唔到，就會係咁迫自己訓，到最後反而瞓唔到。份工本身冇咩壓力，但自己硬係就訓得唔好。<br />\n<br />\n想問下巴打們有冇遇過相似嘅情況，我唔知我應唔應該去搵心理醫生，畢竟咁樣失眠法真係對身體唔好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ecf70947a83eb18a5eeea0e2228802d8c9a58c3b","tid":771212,"uid":30836,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-07T18:04:48.000Z","msg":"你唔洗迫自己瞓 放鬆啲就得"},{"pid":"55a3fc003c73f9cc8e87e009063ec3293285da3e","tid":771212,"uid":144548,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-07T18:05:33.000Z","msg":"fight club"},{"pid":"0b04384f1b3d83176f7412508769e723741c6b08","tid":771212,"uid":37358,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ecf70947a83eb18a5eeea0e2228802d8c9a58c3b","tid":771212,"uid":30836,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-07T18:04:48.000Z","msg":"你唔洗迫自己瞓 放鬆啲就得"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-07T18:07:32.000Z","msg":"我已經坐返係度玩電腦"},{"pid":"59b41a27ff816ec1a89d441673f2a5cb78b17f4f","tid":771212,"uid":30836,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"0b04384f1b3d83176f7412508769e723741c6b08","tid":771212,"uid":37358,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ecf70947a83eb18a5eeea0e2228802d8c9a58c3b","tid":771212,"uid":30836,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-07T18:04:48.000Z","msg":"你唔洗迫自己瞓 放鬆啲就得"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-07T18:0